GLOBAL FOLDER

USAGE NOTE:

As future Developer, Do like this on your own TI,

"FOR DEDICATED PROGRAMS, USE 'CopyVar' AT THE BEGINNING OF THE 'Prgm' TO IMPORT THE LIBRARY FROM THE /Main INTO YOUR /AppFolder, LIKE 'Import' IN PYTHON OR '#Include' IN C."

( Packaging intended to other users, will be the last step. )

FnCheck :
---------
- Find out available locations, before using 'Define'.

Fncheck_lite : ( For packaged Prgm )
--------------
- To Find out available locations to 'Define' in graph mode FUNCTION

Fncheck_3D : ( For packaged Prgm )
--------------
- To Find out available locations to 'Define' in graph mode 3D

InStrng2 :
----------
- Read a string content.
- To develop a text-based command assistant,
- or running a custom font,

ScnDtect :
----------
- Detect the screen configuration.

InitScrn :
----------
- Prepare your screen to PxlMode & restore
( Compatible 89, Titanium, 92, 92+ & V200 )

LoadScrn : ( ScnDtect required )
----------
- A simple LoadScreen.
( Compatible 89, Titanium, 92, 92+ & V200 )

MainClnr:
---------
- initializes essential variables needed for formal calculation.
